  "reference_number": "RUS1565",
  "remarks": "\nJoint-Stock Company ‘IMA Consulting’ is an involved entity within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because it has been awarded a contract to manage the referenda campaigns in non-government controlled areas of Ukraine. Therefore, IMA Consulting is engaging in, providing support for, or promoting a policy or action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
